name: Hive Mind
description:
This is an abstract animation with 72 frames at 8fps.  
I believe everyone has telepathic abilities.  We don't think we're hearing other people's thoughts because we just think we hear our own. I believe we do hear other people's thoughts, it just sounds like our own voice in our heads. This makes it difficult to tell which is which.
